Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.30,0:01:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子 妙子 听说千夏寄来的照片送到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.30,0:01:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 大家一起来看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.27,0:01:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我看 让我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.17,0:01:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪个哪个？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.54,0:01:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拍的很不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看啊 看啊 薰的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.41,0:01:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候可是够辛苦的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.85,0:01:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.18,0:02:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是个活泼的好孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.32,0:02:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能再在一起玩就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.49,0:02:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦 信…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.38,0:02:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.22,0:02:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十九话  膝枕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.86,0:02:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暑假作业还没做完吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.06,0:02:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要教教我不懂的地方就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你去奶奶那里帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.14,0:02:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还一直以为你已经把作业全部做完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.38,0:03:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为千夏去帮忙 奶奶就会非常高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.85,0:03:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年想让她更高兴一些 所以才会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.22,0:03:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了 作业做完之前请让我住在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以啊 千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.33,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么我能做的尽管说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也会帮忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就放心交给我们好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家 谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.28,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 千夏好好地向大家道谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.69,0:03:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也请钿女多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子姐姐住在这样的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从哪个开始做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.75,0:04:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个以后再做 以后再做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.32,0:04:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 先从英语开始努力啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说 该我出场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.30,0:04:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里 蒂娜姐姐 这里不太明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简单 简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.40,0:04:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,英语的形容词分原形、比较级、最高级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.31,0:04:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里就是well、better、best
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.58,0:04:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 在日语里的话就是好、较好、最好这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.72,0:04:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥博多方言比英语更难懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.63,0:05:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.30,0:05:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏 要我帮什么忙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.04,0:05:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 教我不懂的地方就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起 了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.68,0:05:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是妙子的表妹 也是努力的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这加括号 这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.59,0:05:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 进度好快啊 好像也没什么做错的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.79,0:05:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏真是个聪明的好孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.83,0:05:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥 这里 这里我不明白 教教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.91,0:05:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 好 哪里？哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千…千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥 我帮你擦背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.73,0:06:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了 不用帮我擦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.06,0:06:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要害羞嘛 千夏不会在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之不用了 出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏 你干什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.14,0:06:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 不可以给学长添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.03,0:06:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.33,0:06:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏只是想向大哥哥道谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,道谢什么的不用放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.41,0:06:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 因为大哥哥教我做作业 我好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.35,0:07:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 一而再地被大哥哥看到裸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然千夏只有嫁给大哥哥了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和妙子姐姐一样款式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.51,0:07:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实不用勉强来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏只要专心功课就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是大家都教我作业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想稍微报答一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且一天到晚做功课的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏也会累积太多压力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话虽然这么说没错…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以吧 小葵姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.87,0:07:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏如果觉得可以的话 我是没有意见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏 卖力干着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高的地方我来擦吧 很危险的
